snippet.title: Boggled
snippet.description:
Boggled is a place to explore interesting and helpful gems of human knowledge. 

We adore animals – the amazing, the weird and the downright cutest of them all – things such as the largest animals, the cutest animals, the most venomous snakes, the largest dinosaurs and so much more.

We are fascinated by life’s extremes – things such as the strongest women, the most dangerous roads and more.

We also pay attention to celebs – the good, the bad and the ugly that is – and we love digging deeper into beliefs and taboos – things like Amish facts, and things Church of Scientology doesn’t want you to know.

Additionally, we are amazed by riddles, puzzles, brain games, the, history, life hacks, crafts, animated stories, true stories, living healthy and improved lives, attaining peace of mind, and of course – interesting facts!

Subscribe today and hit the notification bell so that you do not miss out on this awesome content.
